# Optional: fine-grained GitHub PAT with the "Plan" read-only user permission.
# Enables the "Official GitHub billing" card (account-wide credit spend,
# straight from the GitHub billing API). Everything else works without it.
# Only useful on individually-paid plans (Pro/Pro+): on Business/Enterprise
# seats the org pays and this user endpoint typically has no data.
# Create one at https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens
GITHUB_COPILOT_BILLING_PAT=
